   Index Cond: (h = 1)
   Remote Filter: (v1 = 1)
(3 rows)

EXPLAIN SELECT * FROM t2 WHERE h = 1 and r = 2 and v1 = 1 and v2 = 2;
                            QUERY PLAN
-------------------------------------------------------------------
 Index Scan using t2_pkey on t2  (cost=0.00..4.12 rows=1 width=20)
   Index Cond: ((h = 1) AND (r = 2))
