-------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Index Scan using t2_v1_v2_idx on t2  (cost=0.00..5.30 rows=10 width=20)
   Index Cond: ((v1 = 1) AND (v2 = 2))
   Remote Filter: (h = 1)
(3 rows)

